content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1261.10 - Loading and unloading of aircraft restricted

State Regulations

No aircraft may be loaded or unloaded except in
designated areas without permission and all passengers must be channeled
through established routes to and from the air terminal. Notes
